i.github.com/users/ldez/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ldez/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ldez/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ldez/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ldez/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ldez/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ldez/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ldez/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2024-11-17T16:10:45Z","updated_at":"2024-11-17T16:10:45Z","body":"> at which point we might even drop the type: source thing, and assume that if makedepends, prepare, and/or build are set, this is of type source\r\n\r\nWe also can assume that the 2 git repos are \"linked\" by the name `foo-bin` `foo`.\r\n\r\n```yml\r\naurs:\r\n  -\r\n    homepage: \"https://example.com/\"\r\n    description: \"Software to create fast and easy drum rolls.\"\r\n    maintainers:\r\n      - \"Foo Bar <foo at bar dot com>\"\r\n    contributors:\r\n      - \"Foo Zaz <foo at zaz dot com>\"\r\n    license: \"MIT\"\r\n    private_key: \"{{ .Env.AUR_KEY }}\"\r\n    skip_upload: true\r\n    commit_author:\r\n      name: goreleaserbot\r\n      email: bot@goreleaser.com\r\n    commit_msg_template: \"pkgbuild updates\"\r\n    git_url_template: \"ssh://aur@aur.archlinux.org/mypackage{{.Suffix}}.git\"\r\n    git_ssh_command: \"ssh -i {{ .Env.KEY }} -o SomeOption=yes\"\r\n    ## Bin only\r\n    bin:\r\n      name: package-bin\r\n      ids:\r\n        - foo\r\n        - bar\r\n      provides:\r\n        - mypackage\r\n      conflicts:\r\n        - otherpkg\r\n      depends: ...\r\n      optdepends: ...\r\n      backup:\r\n        - /etc/foo.conf\r\n      package: ...\r\n    ## Sources only\r\n    sources:\r\n      name: package\r\n      ids:\r\n        - foo\r\n        - bar\r\n      provides:\r\n        - mypackage-bin\r\n      conflicts:\r\n        - otherpkg\r\n      depends:\r\n        - curl\r\n      optdepends: ...\r\n      backup:\r\n        - /etc/foo.conf\r\n      package: ...\r\n      makedepends: ...\r\n      prepare: ...\r\n      build: ...\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\n","author_association":"CONTRIBUTOR","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/goreleaser/goreleaser/issues/comments/2481337486/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"performed_via_github_app":null,"event":"commented","actor":{"login":"ldez","id":5674651,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjU2NzQ2NTE=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/5674651?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/ldez","html_url":"https://github.com/ldez","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ldez/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ldez/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ldez/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ldez/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ldez/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ldez/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ldez/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ldez/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ldez/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false}},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/goreleaser/goreleaser/issues/comments/2481355941","html_url":"https://github.com/goreleaser/goreleaser/issues/5278#issuecomment-2481355941","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/goreleaser/goreleaser/issues/5278","id":2481355941,"node_id":"IC_kwDOBJgEXs6T5nyl","user":{"login":"caarlos0","id":245435,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjI0NTQzNQ==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/245435?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/caarlos0","html_url":"https://github.com/caarlos0","followers_url":"https